{
  "stem": "942.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, I had to put these coats on a table.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a chemical mixed with sawdust that I had to pour this on the fur and sort of rub it, you know, really hard for quite a while, until the shine came up on the fur, you know?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember, it really was hard on my hands, because I didn't have gloves to wear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it must have been some kind of a chemical that was mixed in with the sawdust.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, for me, this was a new venture, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can understand, coming from a little town, all of a sudden, I'm in a big city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In this city, there were about 6,000 Jewish people living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a city, probably, about 20,000 to 25,000 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were street cars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was an opera house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so this was quite a large city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had to deliver fur coats.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, I had two handfuls of coats with addresses, you know, where I had to deliver and get on the street car with these fur coats.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my only pay was the tips that I was getting when I delivered these coats.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, again, every Friday afternoon, I used to get on the train go home for the Sabbath until Sunday morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was quite a big shot, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 13, 14, and I had money in my pocket, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was telling the other kids how life is in this big city, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this went on right up until 1944, early 1944, I guess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in March-- March of 1944, the Germans occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember this transport, this troop-- troop of trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
